      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 23,
      "message": "I may not change this variable as its been used as an original file name which .ofc file moves the content to.\nEx: mv $AAI_PROP_FILE.ofc $AAI_PROP_FILE (This would talk to itself)\n\nI think you mentioned to make it .ofc, as you want to check if .ofc file exists or not before the move operation. \nSo, for that i can check directly in if condition like:\nif [[ -f ${AAI_PROP_FILE}.ofc ]]; then",
